OL,3,CSenedd member 'acted inappropriately'
OL,4,Ctowards women on a work night out
OL,6,FA Welsh politician has been found to
OL,7,Fhave breached the Senedd members' code
OL,8,Fof conduct after acting
OL,9,Finappropriately towards two women on a
OL,10,Fwork's night out.
OL,12,FA Senedd committee report has
OL,13,Frecommended the suspension of MS Rhys
OL,14,Fab Owen who was elected as a Plaid
OL,15,FCymru MS for South Wales Central in
OL,16,F2021.
OL,18,FHe was after a complaint about his
OL,19,Fbehaviour was made. The 37-year-old
OL,20,Fhas sat as an independent in the Welsh
OL,21,FParliament since.
