OL,6,FThe Senedd Standards Commissioner
OL,7,Freport, published today, focuses on a
OL,8,Fnight out at the end of June 2021,
OL,9,Fjust a month after Mr ab Owen had been
OL,10,Felected to the Senedd.
OL,12,FThe report found that Rhys ab Owen was
OL,13,Faccused of verbally abusing a woman
OL,14,Fand inappropriately touching her waist.
OL,16,FWhile in a taxi, he also
OL,17,F"inappropriately touched" a second
OL,18,Fwoman by squeezing her upper thigh
OL,19,Fhard with his hand.
