OL,6,FConcerns were raised within Plaid
OL,7,FCymru the following day, but the
OL,8,Fmatter was not brought to the
OL,9,Fattention of the Senedd's Standards
OL,10,FCommissioner until a year later.
OL,12,FThe Standards Commissioner, who is
OL,13,Findependent, has recommended that Rhys
OL,14,Fab Owen is excluded from the Senedd
OL,15,Ffor 42 calendar days, saying "the
OL,16,FSenedd must be a safe and inclusive
OL,17,Fworkplace, where everybody is treated
OL,18,Fequally."
