OL,6,FThat suspension would be without pay
OL,7,Fand the longest ever handed down in
OL,8,Fthe Senedd's history.
OL,10,FMr ab Owen has admitted being drunk,
OL,11,Fbut has denied inappropriate behaviour.
OL,13,FResponding to the report, Rhys ab Owen
OL,14,Fposted a statement on X which said:
OL,16,F"I would like to apologise to those
OL,17,Fwho were affected by my behaviour on
OL,18,Fthe evening in question, which was not
OL,19,Fup to the standard the public expects
OL,20,Fof a member of the Senedd. And for
OL,21,Fthat, I apologise unreservedly.
