OL,6,F"Whatever challenge I might have with
OL,7,Fthe particulars of the complaint, or
OL,8,Fhow it was subsequently investigated
OL,9,Fis a separate matter, on which I am
OL,10,Fconsidering my next steps. I remain
OL,11,Ffully committed to the Senedd and to
OL,12,Fmy work there on behalf of my
OL,13,Fconstituents.
OL,15,F"I would like to thank my wife and
OL,16,Ffamily for the love and support which
OL,17,Fkept me going throughout this
OL,18,Fdifficult and drawn out process. I
OL,19,Fhave made changes to my lifestyle that
OL,20,Fare helping me become a better person
OL,21,Fand representative.
