OL,6,F"I will not be making any further
OL,7,Fcomments at this time and I ask that
OL,8,Fthe privacy of y family and everyone
OL,9,Felse involved is respected."
OL,11,FA Plaid Cymru spokesperson has said
OL,12,Fthe party is taking 'swift and
OL,13,Fappropriate action in response' to the
OL,14,Freport and Rhys ab Owen has now been
OL,15,Fsuspended from the party as well as
OL,16,Fthe Senedd group.
