OL,6,F"In light of the conclusions of the
OL,7,Freport, Rhys ab Owen MS's membership
OL,8,Fof the party has been suspended
OL,9,Fpending the outcome of an internal
OL,10,Fprocess that will commence immediately.
OL,12,F"The report follows a lengthy
OL,13,Finvestigation and comes to a series of
OL,14,Fconclusions regarding the behaviour of
OL,15,Fthe Member.
