OL,6,F"It also references shortcomings in
OL,7,Fthe party's processes which pre-dates
OL,8,F'Prosiect Pawb' ` a wholesale review
OL,9,Fof Plaid Cymru's practices and
OL,10,Fculture. Decisive action has been
OL,11,Ftaken to implement the recommendations
OL,12,Fand strengthen the party's governance."
OL,14,FSenedd members are expected to discuss
OL,15,Fthe report in next Wednesday's plenary
OL,16,Fsession.
